column5: This map is great for finding small trails. Consider me brookie fishing today!  http://ofsc.mapbase.ca/viewer/
Cool, Chad.  I got us an awesome Largie lake and maybe some access to Muskie heaven.
Amazing.  Thanks a ton for this.  I've seen my lake appear on a non-satellite image based map only a couple of times and seen it named only one other time...this is awesome!
Used this a few times.  Landed me nothin' but a few nice hikes.
I can't get this thing to work....clicked on terms of use...accepted...and now I just have a blank screen...ads on the right side...header on the top....no map!
Maybe your internet settings need to be adjusted?? Or an old version of IE??
Probably the settings....pretty sure its IE8...one of these crazy IT guys just upgraded my workstation...so it's all wonky now
IT guys are always screwing with us non- IT types. Haha
